<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Fan2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Fan,</orth> vb. 1) to blow as with a fan: <bibl n="shak. ven 52" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 52" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 52</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.176" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 176</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.142" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.2.128" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 2, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.375" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 375</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III Chor.</bibl> 6 (O. Edd. <cit><quote>fayning).</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.212" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 212</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 3, 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.2.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 2, 50</bibl>.<lb />2) to winnow, to try: <cit><quote>the love I bear him made me to f. you thus,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.177" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 177</bibl></cit>.
